Copy contents of ceilometer directory to rpmbuild dir:
cp -R ceilometer/* /root/rpmbuild/

Build venv via anvil:
/home/anvil/smithy --venv-deploy-dir=/opt/openstack/ -p conf/personas/in-a-box/venv-all.yaml -o conf/origins/kilo-venv-2015.1.0.yaml -a prepare -j 1 --distros-patch=conf/distros/venv-patch.json

Create source tarball:
cd /home/openstack/ceilometer/venv
mkdir ceilometer-<version> #example: ceilometer-2015.1.0.3
cp ceilometer-<version>-<release>-venv.tar.gz ceilometer-<version> #example: ceilometer-2015.1.0.3-1-venv.tar.gz ceilometer-2015.1.0.3
tar -zcvf ceilometer-<version>.tar.gz ceilometer-<version> #example: ceilometer-2015.1.0.3.tar.gz ceilometer-2015.1.0.3

Copy it to the rpmbuild/Sources dir:
cp ceilometer-<version>.tar.gz /root/rpmbuild/SOURCES/ #example: ceilometer-2015.1.0.3.tar.gz

Build using the spec:
rpmbuild -bb /root/rpmbuild/SPECS/openstack-ceilometer.spec
